public interface ExistenceBOM
extends BusinessObjectModule

Infrastructure depends on BusinessObjectModule implementation for every business object type to determine if it exist.

Infrastructure delegates the responsibility to individual Business Object Module(BOM) implementation to determine if a business object already exist in the system. Every BOM which needs to be migrated, need to provide its specific implementation.
